author: Minecraft
description:
The real story of Minecraft has always been a total mystery… until now. The Narrator is investigating, and he’s leaving no block unbroken. Is the Nether beneath the Overworld? Why do Endermen hate eye contact? And why does the Nether have a “roof”?! 

Jens Bergensten and Kevin Grace take the hot seat to answer these questions and more... with questions of their own. 

What’s your favorite Minecraft theory?
title: THE UNTOLD MYSTERY OF MINECRAFT
